## Observations

- Multiple failed login attempts detected
- Same user targeted repeatedly
- Same source IP involved in attempts
- Login pattern shows repeated authentication failures

---

## Findings

- Possible brute force login activity
- Repeated authentication failures from same source
- Suspicious login behavior on target account

---

## Indicators of Compromise (IOCs)

- Event IDs: 4624, 4625
- Source IP: X.X.X.X
- Target account: [username]

